      "We couldn't process your Creative Cloud files about 5 minutes ago due to a connection issue. Select 'Try again' to reprocess your files, or contact your IT administrator if the problem continues. This interface works with all assistive technology."
      
      **Why this works:**
      - Short, clear sentences (6th-grade reading level)
      - No unnecessary words or corporate language  
